ced%20at%20a%20local%20Merle%20Norman%20the%20second%20I%20turned%20the%20pre-approved%20age.%20Like%20many%20of%20my%20peers%2C%20I%20stood%20back%20while%20the%20makeup%20saleswoman%20took%20aim%20at%20my%20two%20lobes%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpiercing-myths-to-stop-believing-2018-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epiercing%20gun%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20kids%20decided%20they%20wanted%20to%20get%20their%20ears%20pierced%2C%20I%20opted%20to%20take%20them%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-getting-ear-styled-by-professional-lulus-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprofessional%20piercing%20studio%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20walked%20past%20the%20tattoo%20studio%20below%2C%20walls%20papered%20with%20seemingly%20infinite%20options%20while%20people%20mulled%20their%20choices%20over%20and%20up%20the%20narrow%20wooden%20stairs%20to%20the%20friendly%20staff%20who%20helped%20us%20navigate%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20wanted%20my%20kids%20to%20have%20the%20safest%20experience%20possible%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20reason%20I%20insisted%20we%20go%20to%20a%20piercing%20studio%20was%20for%20quality%20and%20hygiene.%20The%20Association%20of%20Professional%20Piercers%20warns%20that%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsafepiercing.org%2Fpicking-your-piercer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMost%20ear-piercing%20guns%20can't%20be%20sterilized%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20anyone%20being%20pierced%20by%20them%20is%20at%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20not%20just%20them%20who%20recommend%20not%20using%20piercing%20guns.%20In%20an%20article%20for%20Johns%20Hopkins%20on%20how%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hopkinsmedicine.org%2Fhealth%2Fwellness-and-prevention%2Fhow-to-safely-get-your-childs-ears-pierced%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esafely%20get%20your%20kid's%20ears%20pierced%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20pediatrician%20Rac