0myself.%20Not%20with%20anyone%20else.%20I%20mean%2C%20I%20want%20to%20win%20when%20I%20play%20my%20wife%20in%20tennis.%20I%20want%20to%20win%20against%20my%20son%20in%20chess.%20I%20fancy%20myself%20a%20great%20Scrabble%20player.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20when%20you%20saw%20Sudeikis%20playing%20Shane%2C%20you%20weren't%20bitter%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo.%20Not%20at%20all.%20I%20believe%20roles%20come%20into%20your%20life.%20I've%20never%20missed%20out%20on%20a%20role.%20I%20haven't%20gotten%20a%20number%20of%20roles%20I%20really%20wanted%2C%20but%20I%20wasn't%20right%20for%20them%2C%20and%20the%20people%20that%20missed%20out%20on%20roles%20that%20I've%20gotten%2C%20I%20hope%20they%20feel%20the%20same%20way.%20It%20ebbs%20and%20flows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20thing%20that%20I%20have%20going%20for%20me%2C%20and%20this%20is%20a%20lesson%20that%20I%20learned%20early%20in%20my%2020s%2C%20is%20that%20I%20don't%20look%20in%20other%20people's%20lanes.%20I'm%20in%20my%20lane.%20I'm%20not%20competing%20against%20anyone.%20How%20can%20you%3F%20I%20am%20authentic%20to%20me.%20What%20I%20have%20to%20give%2C%20only%20I%20have%20to%20give.%20No%20one%20else%20is%20giving%20what%20I%20have%20to%20give.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20my%20own%20author%20of%20what%20I%20have%20to%20share.%20And%20I%20love%20to%20see%20other%20people's%20work%3B%20I'm%20not%20threatened%20by%20that%20at%20all.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2012%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20fascinating%20years%20in%20your%20filmography%20because%20you%20have%20a%20role%20in%20Steven%20Spielberg's%20%26quot%3BLincoln%26quot%3B%20and%20Quentin%20Tarantino's%20%26quot%3BDjango%20Unchained.%26quot%3B%20Two%20legends%2C%20but%20also%20two%20directors%20who%20I%20have%20to%20imagine%20are%20vastly%20different%20on%20set.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVery%20different%20vibes.%20Steven%20wears%20a%20tie%20to%20work%20every%20day.%20He's%20very%20passionate%2C%20but%20he's%20reserved.%20He's