e%20CVs%20you%20wouldn't%20typically%20find%20in%20an%20EPL%20boardroom%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0including%20Ian%20Graham%2C%20who%20holds%20a%20doctorate%20in%20physics%20from%20Cambridge%20and%20who%20headed%20up%20Liverpool's%20research%20department%20until%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Google%20DeepMind%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6616ac3d1caec1275a6e8476%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDeepMind%20researchers%20Zhe%20Wang%20and%20Petar%20Veli%C4%8Dkovi%C4%87%20at%20Liverpool%20FC's%20stadium%2C%20Anfield.%3Cp%3EGoogle%20DeepMind%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20that%20knowledge%20on%20hand%20helped%20the%20collaboration%20between%20DeepMind%20and%20Liverpool%20to%20run%20smoothly%2C%20according%20to%20Veli%C4%8Dkovi%C4%87.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20past%2010%20years%20or%20so%2C%20Liverpool%20have%20had%20people%20on%20their%20team%20with%20Ph.D.s%20from%20Cambridge%20and%20Harvard%20%E2%80%94%20these%20are%20people%20who%20are%20very%20engineering%2C%20data%2C%20and%20research-minded%2C%20and%20they've%20worked%20on%20using%20statistical%20analysis%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20there%20was%20already%20a%20good%2C%20solid%20foundation%20we%20could%20build%20on%20with%20deep%20learning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiverpool's%20experts%20helped%20DeepMind%20to%20judge%20whether%20TacticAI's%20corner%20routines%20were%20effective%2C%20while%20the%20two%20organizations%20have%20also%20teamed%20up%20to%20produce%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeepmind.google%2Fdiscover%2Fblog%2Fadvancing-sports-analytics-through-ai-research%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebroader%20study%20about%20AI's%20role%20in%20soccer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D6456940027a0b7e9b7889fa31f6b9d38d5ae1c3f4979e563366c29fcaa585cdc%26po