s.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbattleground-pennsylvania-trump-holds-rally-biden-plans-tax-speech-as-rematch-heats-up%2Famp_articleshow%2F109269816.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbattleground-pennsylvania-trump-holds-rally-biden-plans-tax-speech-as-rematch-heats-up%2Famp_articleshow%2F109269816.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20Will%20Get%20More%20Seats%20In%202024%20Compared%20To%202019%20Polls%3A%20P%20Chidambaram%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESenior%20Congress%20leader%20P%20Chidambaram%20today%20asserted%20that%20his%20party%20would%20get%20more%20seats%20in%20the%20ensuing%20elections%20than%20in%202019%20and%20predicted%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20would%20secure%20a%20resounding%20victory%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20also%20said%20that%20neither%20Hinduism%20nor%20the%20Hindus%20were%20under%20any%20threat%20and%20it%20was%20the%20BJP's%20%26quot%3Bcalculated%20strategy%26quot%3B%20to%20paint%20the%20entire%20Opposition%20as%20%26quot%3Banti-Hindu%26quot%3B%20to%20project%20PM%20Modi%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bsaviour%20of%20Hindus%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20described%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20TMC%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bkey%20player%26quot%3B%20in%20this%20election%20and%20said%20that%20her%20ability%20to%20hold%20the%20fort%20in%20the%20state%20will%20strengthen%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20speak%20for%20all%20the%20states.%20I%20can%20confidently%20predict%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20will%20record%20a%20resounding%20victory%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20In%20Kerala%2C%20the%20two%20fronts%20(UDF%20and%20LDF)%20will%20share%20the%2020%20seats%2C%20leaving%20nothing%20to%20the%20BJP.%20In%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana%2C%20the%20Congress%20governments%20are%20popular%20and%20Congress%20will%20get%20many%20more%20seats%20than%20in%202019%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20won%2052%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20the%20Congress%20may%20show%20an%20improved%20performance%2C%20he%20claimed%20there%20are%20also%20encouraging%20reports%20about%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20from%20Haryana%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Jharkhand%20and%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20Congressman%20said%20that%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20accusing%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20of%20appeasement%20politics%20and%20calling%20them%20a%20%26quot%3Bband%20of%20anti-Hindu%20politicians%20bent%20on%20breaking%20India%20up%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20BJP's%20strategy%20for%20the%20ensuing%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20BJP's%20calculated%20strategy%20to%20paint%20the%20entire%20Opposition%20as%20anti-Hindu%20and%20to%20boost%20Narendra%20Modi's%20credentials%20as%20the%20saviour%20of%20Hindus.%20Hinduism%20is%20not%20in%20danger%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20opined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20could%20be%20a%20factor%20in%20the%20ensuing%20election%2C%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BUndoubtedly%2C%20she%20is%20a%20key%20player%20in%20this%20election.%20Her%20ability%20to%20hold%20the%20fort%20in%20West%20Bengal%20will%20strengthen%20the%20INDIA%20combination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20said%20that%20the%20Kachchatheevu%20issue%20was%20%26quot%3Bclosed%26quot%3B%20and%20questioned%20the%20BJP's%20timing%20of%20raising%20the%20issue%20when%20the%20elections%20were%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKachchatheevu%20is%20a%20closed%20issue.%20The%20agreement%20was%20reached%2050%20years%20ago.%20PM%20Modi%20has%20been%20in%20office%20since%202014%3B%20why%20did%20he%20not%20raise%20the%20issue%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Union%20minister%20q