PM%20Modi%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNeed%20To%20Check%20Temperament%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex-Selector%20On%20Why%20Mayank%20Isn't%20Yet%20Ready%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EYoung%20tearaway%20pacer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mayank%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F115355-mayank-yadav-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMayank%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20taken%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20by%20storm%20with%20his%20undeniable%20pace.%20On%20his%20IPL%20debut%20for%20the%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20(LSG)%2C%20Mayank%20bowled%20the%20fastest%20delivery%20of%20IPL%202024%2C%20clocked%20at%20155.8%20kmph%2C%20against%20the%20Punjab%20Kings.%20In%20the%20very%20next%20game%20against%20the%20RCB%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20better%20that%20record%20with%20delivery%20clocked%20at%20156.7%20kmph.%20His%20performance%20has%20already%20earned%20him%20backing%20of%20several%20experts%20for%20a%20place%20in%20India's%20squad%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBu%2C%20Mayank%20has%20missed%20the%20last%20two%20games%20for%20LSG%20due%20to%20a%20workload%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevang%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20head%20coach%20of%20Delhi's%20Ranji%20Trophy%20team%2C%20feels%20Mayank%2C%20a%20player%20who%20has%20followed%20from%20close%20quarters%2C%20hasn't%20ticked%20all%20boxes%20yet%20to%20become%20eligible%20for%20an%20India%20cap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20feels%20that%20a%20player%20like%20Mayank%2C%20who%20is%20susceptible%20to%20injuries%2C%20needs%20to%20play%20more%20games%20to%20justify%20his%20fitness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20a%20special%20talent.%20Somebody%20who%20clocks%20155%20kmph%20is%20definitely%20special.%20So%20obviously%2C%20with%20the%20impact%20that%20the%20body%20goes%20through%2C%20there%20will%20be%20injuries%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20that%20they%20can't%20be%20managed.%20There%20has%20to%20be%20a%20way%20of%20grooming%20him.%20He%20will%20have%20to%20play%20more%20matches%20and%20go%20through%20the%20rigours%2C%20and%20then%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20assessed%20as%20to%20how%20he%20is%20able%20to%20withstand%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Gandhi%20told%20Sports%20Now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20he%20has%20to%20tick%20all%20the%20boxes%20if%20he%20wants%20to%20play%20for%20India%20in%20the%20upcoming%20World%20Cup.%20He%20can%20be%20better%20accessed%20if%20he%20can%20play%20all%2012%20or%2014%20matches%20in%20the%20IPL.%20Selectors%20need%20to%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20parameters%2C%20and%20if%20he%20is%20able%20to%20tick%20most%20of%20those%20boxes%2C%20then%20he%20will%20merit%20a%20selection.%20Then%20again%2C%20the%20ball%20is%20in%20Mayank's%20court%2C%20and%20he%20has%20to%20prove%20himself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20also%20suggested%20that%20Mayank%20had%20a%20surprise%20factor%20during%20his%20first%20two%20IPL%20games%2C%20but%20the%20opposition%20teams%20might%20work%20out%20a%20way%20to%20tackle%20him.%20In%20that%20case%2C%20the%20former%20India%20selector%20feels%20that%20the%2021-year-old%20will%20have%20to%20work%20more%20on%20his%20bowling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSelectors%20also%20need%20to%20check%20his%20temperament%20and%20how%20he%20bounces%20back%20after%20an%20off%20day.%20Consistency%20in%20fitness%20and%20temperament%20are%20the%20other%20aspects%20that%20selectors%20will%20look%20at.%20Initially%2C%20he%20had%20the%20surprise%20element%20working%20in%20his%20favour%2C%20but%20now%20batters%20and%20think%20tanks%20will%20try%20to%20work%20out%20how%20to%20face%20him.%20So%2C%20how%20he%20manages%20to%20overcome%20that%20hurdle%20will%20be%20key.%20So%20Yadav%20has%20to%20tick%20two%20more%20boxes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712997780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Frcoe6dc_mayank-yadav_625x300_30_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fneed-to-check-his-temperament-ex-bcci-selectors-big-statement-on-mayank-yadav-and-why-he-is-not-yet-ready-for-india-5432302%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mayank%20Yadav's%20performance%20has%20already%20earned%20him%20backing%20of%20several%20experts%20for%20a%20place%20in%20India's%20squad%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'What%20have%20you%20done...'%3A%20Priyanka%20slams%20BJP%20for%20blaming%20Cong%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712997773000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109267391%2Cimgsize-43774.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fpriyanka-gandhi-attacks-bjp-how-long-will-you-keep-blaming-congress-you-have-been-in-power-for-last-10-years%2Farticleshow%2F109267322.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20criticized%20the%20BJP%2C%20questioning%20their%20continuous%20blame%20on%20the%20Congress%20despite%20being%20out%20of%20power%20for%20a%20decade.%20She%20highlighted%20the%20significant%20role%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20played%20in%20establishing%20institutions%20like%20IITs%2C%20IIMs%2C%20and%20AIIMs.%20Vadra%20alleged%20PM%20Modi%20neglected%20Uttarakhand%20during%20a%20recent%20natural%20disaster%2C%20stating%20that%20no%20relief%20funds%20were%20provided%20for%20restoration%20efforts%20in%20the%20region%20she%20refers%20to%20as%20Dev%20Bhoomi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Young%20People%20Getting%20Are%20Unhappier%20With%20Time%20-%20Reason%3A%20Lack%20Of%20Freedom%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExperts%20often%20highlight%20social%20media%20and%20harsh%20economic%20times%20as%20key%20reasons%20why%20young%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Furl.uk.m.mimecastprotect.com%2Fs%2FZRVqCg5jjh160qwUYQwqF%3Fdomain%3Dtheconversationuk.cmail20.com%5C%22%3Epeople%20are%20getting%20unhappier%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20while%20those%20factors%20are%20important%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20emphasise%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYounger%20generations%20have%20less%20freedom%20and%20independence%20than%20previous%20generations%20did.%20The%20area%20where%20children%20are%20allowed%20to%20range%20unsupervised%20outside%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fassets.childrenscommissioner.gov.uk%2Fwpuploads%2F2018%2F08%2FPlay-final-report.pdf%5C%22%3Ehas%20shrunk%20by%2090%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20the%201970s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParents%20increasingly%20organise%20entertainment%20%E2%80%93%20ranging%20from%20play%20dates%20and%20sports%20and%20music%20classes%20to%20family%20cinema%20trips%20%E2%80%93%20for%20their%20children%2C%20rather%20than%20letting%20them%20come%20up%20with%20it%20themselves.%20Perhaps%20this%20can%20help%20explain%20recent%20reports%20that%20many%20teenagers%20today%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Flifeandstyle%2F2024%2Ffeb%2F10%2Fmeet-generation-stay-at-home-dont-pay-to-go-clubbing-watch-it-at-home-on-your-phone%5C%22%3Echoose%20to%20be%20holed%20up%20in%20their%20bedrooms%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20childhood%20freedom%20isn't%20just%20a%20result%20of%20parental%20control.%20Societal%20expectations%20and%20school%20policies%20also%20have%20huge%20influences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20constraints%20to%20freedom%20often%20stem%20from%20well-meaning%20intentions%2C%20such%20as%20safety%20concerns%20(location%20tracking%2C%20for%20example)%20or%20cultural%20norms.%20Understandably%2C%20nobody%20wants%20to%20be%20the%20parent%20who%20lets%20their%20kid%20take%20(perceived)%20risks%20if%20others%20don't.%20But%20there%20are%20risks%20to%20over-protecting%20children%20too.%20It%20can%20inadvertently%20hinder%20their%20psychological%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EEmotional%2C%20social%20and%20cognitive%20effects%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPsychologist%20Jean%20Piaget%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20exploration%20and%20experimentation%20in%20cognitive%20development%20in%20the%201950s.%20He%20noted%20that%20children%20construct%20their%20understanding%20of%20the%20world%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpsycnet.apa.org%2Frecord%2F2007-10742-000%5C%22%3Ethrough%20active%20engagement%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20their%20environment.%20By%20restricting%20children's%20freedom%20to%20explore%20and%20take%20age-appropriate%20risks%2C%20we%20deprive%20them%20of%20opportunities%20for%20intellectual%20curiosity%20and%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lack%20of%20independence%20can%20undermine%20young%20people's%20sense%20of%20agency%20and%20control%20over%20their%20lives.%20And%20research%20in%20psychology%20consistently%20demonstrates%20that%20when%20people%2C%20young%20or%20old%2C%20feel%20powerless%20and%20constrained%20by%20external%20forces%2C%20such%20as%20parental%20supervision%20or%20societal%20expectations%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpositivepsychology.com%2Flearned-helplessness-seligman-theory-depression-cure%2F%5C%22%3Eit%20can%20lead%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20frustration%2C%20helplessness%20and%20low%20self-esteem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20autonomy%20limits%20young%20people's%20opportunities%20for%20self-discovery%2C%20creativity%20and%20personal%20growth.%20When%20children%20are%20constantly%20guided%20and%20supervised%2C%20they%20miss%20out%20on%20the%20invaluable%20experiences%20of%20problem-solving%2C%20decision-making%20and%20learning%20from%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decline%20in%20independence%20can%20have%20implications%20for%20social%20and%20emotional%20development.%20Children%20may%20get%20love%2C%20support%20and%20attention%20within%20the%20family%20unit.%20But%20spending%20too%20much%20time%20with%20parents%20may%20lead%20to%20difficulties%20getting%20on%20with%20peers%2C%20who%20don't%20provide%20the%20same%20unconditional%20love%20and%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20when%20children%20are%20constantly%20surrounded%20by%20adults%20and%20structured%20activities%2C%20they%20may%20struggle%20to%20develop%20meaningful%20relationships%2C%20assertiveness%20and%20resilience.%20Research%20highlights%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1002%2F9780470147658.chpsy0310%5C%22%3Eimportance%20of%20peer%20interactions%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20shaping%20social%20competence%20and%20emotional%20intelligence.%20After%20all%2C%20parents%20may%20not%20require%20you%20to%20empathise%20with%20them%2C%20but%20friends%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20orchestrating%20play%20dates%20and%20entertainment%2C%20parents%20may%20therefore%20inadvertently%20limit%20their%20children's%20ability%20to%20navigate%20social%20dynamics.%20This%20will%20include%20learning%20empathy%20and%20developing%20interpersonal%20skills%20independently.%20It%20will%20also%20set%20an%20expectation%20that%20children%20will%20come%20to%20internalise%20the%20idea%20that%20%E2%80%9Cparents%20will%20do%20things%20so%20I%20don't%20have%20to%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20leading%20to%20further%20lack%20of%20accomplishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20independence%20can%20also%20contribute%20to%20feelings%20of%20boredom%2C%20restlessness%20and%20disengagement.%20Humans%20need%20to%20be%20engaged%20in%20activities%20that%20challenge%20and%20absorb%20our%20attention%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F224927532_Flow_The_Psychology_of_Optimal_Experience%5C%22%3Eleading%20to%20feelings%20of%20fulfilment%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20happiness.%20When%20children%20are%20constantly%20entertained%20and%20supervised%2C%20they%20may%20struggle%20to%20find%20activities%20that%20naturally%20capture%20their%20interest%20and%20provide%20a%20sense%20of%20purpose%20and%20enjoyment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20important.%20In%20defining%20happiness%2C%20positive%20psychology%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpsycnet.apa.org%2Frecord%2F2002-18216-000%5C%22%3Eemphasises%20both%20the%20emotional%20aspect%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20experiencing%20positive%20emotions%2C%20and%20the%20cognitive%20aspect%2C%20which%20involves%20a%20sense%20of%20overall%20satisfaction%20with%20one's%20life%2C%20including%20meaning%20and%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearch%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F353260333_Putting_parental_overprotection_into_a_family_systems_context_Relations_of_overprotective_parenting_with_perceived_coparenting_and_adolescent_anxiety%5C%22%3Ehas%20shown%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20parenting%20that%20supports%20autonomy%2C%20encouraging%20children%20to%20make%20their%20own%20decisions%20and%20take%20responsibility%20for%20their%20actions%2C%20is%20linked%20to%20better%20psychological%20wellbeing%20in%20adolescents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConversely%2C%20excessive%20parental%20control%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F34630207%2F%5C%22%3Eis%20associated%20with%3C%2Fa%3E%20higher%20levels%20of%20emotional%20distress%20and%20lower%20levels%20of%20life%20satisfaction%20among%20adolescents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20school%20environment%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F13632752.2023.2255403%5C%22%3Ealso%20plays%20a%20significant%20role%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Zero-tolerance%20policies%2C%20strict%20disciplinary%20measures%20and%20standardised%20testing%20are%20commonplace.%20But%20overly%20strict%20and%20punitive%20disciplinary%20practices%20are%20associated%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC6685139%2F%5C%22%3Edecreased%20intrinsic%20motivation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20academic%20engagement%20among%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20developments%20in%20response%20to%20safety%20concerns%2C%20such%20as%20increased%20surveillance%20and%20monitoring%20within%20schools%2C%20further%20intrude%20upon%20students'%20autonomy%20and%20independence.%20Metal%20detectors%2C%20security%20cameras%20and%20random%20searches%20ultimately%20create%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20surveillance%20and%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EAge-appropriate%20freedom%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvidence%20supports%20the%20idea%20that%20freedom%20and%20independence%20is%20crucial%20for%20the%20happiness%20and%20wellbeing%20of%20young%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20ways%20to%20let%20your%20children%20have%20age-appropriate%20freedoms.%20A%20five-year-old%2C%20for%20example%2C%20can%20be%20allowed%20and%20encouraged%20to%20butter%20their%20own%20toast%2C%20make%20their%20bed%2C%20or%20play%20on%20their%20own%20in%20the%20garden.%20A%2010-year-old%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20should%20be%20able%20to%20walk%20to%20and%20from%20school%20on%20their%20own%2C%20be%20responsible%20for%20their%20homework%20and%20keep%20their%20space%20tidy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20children%20reach%20the%20age%20of%2015%2C%20you%20can%20encourage%20them%20to%20cook%20a%20family%20meal%2C%20do%20laundry%20and%20arrange%20travel%20to%20school%2C%20clubs%20or%20friends'%20houses%20independently%20rather%20than%20be%20chauffeured%20by%20their%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20also%20be%20useful%20to%20decline%20to%20provide%20entertainment%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20letting%20them%20work%20something%20out%20on%20their%20own.%20Children%20are%20wonderfully%20creative%20and%20if%20there%20is%20nothing%20to%20do%2C%20they%20will%20often%20think%20of%20something%20eventually.%20This%20could%20even%20apply%20to%20play%20dates.%20It%20is%20OK%20to%20invite%20a%20child's%20friend%20over%20with%20no%20specific%20entertainment%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20forward%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20promote%20environments%20that%20foster%20autonomy%2C%20self-expression%20and%20independent%20learning%2C%20both%20at%20home%20and%20in%20educational%20institutions%2C%20to%20support%20the%20development%20and%20happiness%20of%20young%20people.%3Cimg%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22no-referrer-when-downgrade%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F226933%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E(%3Cstrong%3EAuthor%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fprofiles%2Ffiorentina-sterkaj-1515346%5C%22%3EFiorentina%20Sterkaj%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Senior%20Lecturer%2C%20Department%20of%20Psychological%20Sciences%2C%20School%20of%20Psychology%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Finstitutions%2Funiversity-of-east-london-924%5C%22%3EUniversity%20of%20East%20London%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E(%3Cstrong%3EDisclosure%20Statement%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3EFiorentina%20Sterkaj%20does%20not%20work%20for%2C%20consult%2C%20own%20shares%20in%20or%20receive%20funding%20from%20any%20company%20or%20organisation%20that%20would%20benefit%20from%20this%20article%2C%20and%20has%20disclosed%20no%20relevant%20affiliations%20beyond%20their%20academic%20appointment)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20license.%20Read%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fyoung-people-are-getting-unhappier-a-lack-of-childhood-freedom-and-independence-may-be-partly-to-blame-226933%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20a