canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-australia-68805652%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sydney%20mall%20attack%3A%20'It%20was%20insanity'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712995791000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F16E4D%2Fproduction%2F_133137739_p0hqln45.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-68805652%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Eyewitnesses%20tell%20of%20their%20horror%20as%20a%20deadly%20knife%20attack%20sparked%20panic%20at%20a%20Sydney%20shopping%20mall.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-australia-68805652%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Country%20Has%20Highest%20Living%20Cost%20In%20All%20Of%20Asia.%20Inflation%20Rate%20At%2025%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan%20has%20the%20highest%20living%20cost%20in%20all%20of%20Asia%20with%20a%2025%20per%20cent%20inflation%20rate%20and%20its%20economy%20may%20grow%20at%20the%20fourth%20lowest%20pace%20of%201.9%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20region%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20Asian%20Development%20Bank%20(ADB)%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20was%20released%20on%20Thursday%20in%20Philippines's%20capital%20Manila.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20Express%20Tribune%20reported%20that%2C%20the%20Asian%20Development%20Outlook%20also%20painted%20a%20gloomy%20picture%20for%20the%20next%20fiscal%20year%20as%20well%2C%20projecting%2015%20per%20cent%20inflation%20rate%20for%20the%20next%20fiscal%20year%20-%20again%20the%20highest%20among%2046%20countries%20and%20a%202.8%20per%20cent%20growth%20rate%20-%20the%20fifth%20lowest%20for%20FY%202024-25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manila-based%20lending%20agency%20stated%20that%20the%20inflation%20rate%20in%20Pakistan%20is%20expected%20to%20be%2025%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20current%20fiscal%20year%20-%20the%20highest%20in%20all%20of%20Asia.%20This%20makes%20Pakistan%20the%20most%20expensive%20nation%20in%20Asia.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20Pakistan%20used%20to%20be%20the%20highest%20in%20South%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Bank%20of%20Pakistan%20(SBP)%20and%20federal%20government%20had%20set%20the%20inflation%20target%20at%2021%20per%20cent%20for%20this%20fiscal%20year%20but%20they%20are%20going%20to%20miss%20it%20despite%20inflicting%20huge%20losses%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20a%2022%20per%20cent%20interest%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ADB%20said%20during%20the%20current%20fiscal%20year%2C%20the%20country's%20economic%20growth%20rate%20might%20remain%20at%201.9%20per%20cent%20--%20the%20fourth%20lowest%20after%20Myanmar%2C%20Azerbaijan%20and%20Nauru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20is%20in%20a%20stagflation%20phase%20for%20a%20prolonged%20period%20and%20the%20World%20Bank%20too%20said%20last%20week%20that%20another%2010%20million%20more%20people%20might%20fall%20into%20the%20poverty%20trap%20because%20of%20any%20adverse%20shocks.%20About%2098%20million%20people%20are%20already%20living%20a%20poor%20life%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20the%20ADB%20gave%20a%20rather%20optimistic%20economic%20scenario%20close%20to%20Pakistan's%20official%20forecasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20latest%20ADB%20report%20stated%20that%20Pakistan%20would%20continue%20to%20face%20challenges%20from%20substantial%20new%20external%20financing%20requirements%20and%20the%20rollover%20of%20old%20debt%2C%20exacerbated%20by%20tight%20global%20monetary%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manila-based%20lender%20said%20political%20uncertainty%20that%20affected%20macroeconomic%20policy%20making%20would%20remain%20a%20key%20risk%20to%20the%20sustainability%20of%20stabilisation%20and%20reform%20efforts.%20It%20said%20with%20Pakistan's%20large%20external%20financing%20requirements%20and%20weak%20external%20buffers%2C%20disbursement%20from%20multilateral%20and%20bilateral%20partners%20remained%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurther%20IMF%20support%20for%20a%20medium-term%20reform%20agenda%20would%20considerably%20improve%20market%20sentiment%20and%20catalyse%20affordable%20external%20financing%20from%20other%20sources%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinance%20Minister%20Muhammad%20Aurangzeb%20is%20set%20to%20meet%20the%20IMF%20Managing%20Director%20Kristalina%20Georgieva%20next%20week%20in%20Washington%20to%20request%20a%20new%20bailout%20package.%20The%20IMF%20MD%20said%20this%20week%20that%20Pakistan%20was%20in%20discussions%20for%20a%20potential%20follow%20up%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20said%20that%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Bvery%20important%20issues%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20solved%20in%20Pakistan%3A%20the%20tax%20base%2C%20how%20the%20richer%20part%20of%20the%20society%20contributed%20to%20the%20economy%2C%20the%20way%20public%20spending%20is%20being%20directed%2C%20and%20creating%20a%20more%20transparent%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ADB%20said%20low%20confidence%2C%20a%20surge%20in%20living%20costs%2C%20and%20the%20implementation%20of%20tighter%20macroeconomic%20policies%20under%20the%20IMF%20programme%20would%20restrain%20domestic%20demand%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20government's%20goal%20was%20to%20achieve%20a%20primary%20surplus%20of%200.4per%20cent%20and%20an%20overall%20deficit%20of%207.5per%20cent%20of%20GDP%20in%20FY2024%2C%20with%20both%20declining%20gradually%20in%20subsequent%20years.%20However%2C%20the%20World%20Bank%20said%20last%20week%20that%20Pakistan%20would%20miss%20both%20these%20budget%20targets%2C%20reported%20The%20Express%20Tribune.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicate