lotted%20to%20his%20firm%20under%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20excise%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%2C%20Ms%20Kavitha%20had%20told%20Mr%20Reddy%20that%20in%20case%20he%20does%20not%20pay%20the%20amount%20to%20the%20ruling%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20his%20business%20will%20be%20harmed%20in%20Telangana%20and%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%2C%20who%20was%20an%20accused%20in%20a%20money-laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20scam%20in%20Delhi%2C%20had%20turned%20an%20approver%20in%20the%20case%20that%20is%20being%20probed%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED).%20The%20CBI%20is%20yet%20to%20file%20a%20charge-sheet%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeking%20the%20BRS%20leader's%20custodial%20interrogation%2C%20the%20CBI%20told%20Special%20Judge%20Kaveri%20Baweja%20that%20it%20was%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Binsistence%20and%20assurance%26quot%3B%20of%20Ms%20Kavitha%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20former%20Telangana%20chief%20minister%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%2C%20that%20Mr%20Reddy%20got%20involved%20in%20the%20liquor%20business%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Kavitha%20had%20allegedly%20assured%20Mr%20Reddy%20that%20she%20had%20contacts%20in%20the%20Delhi%20government%20and%20that%20she%20would%20help%20him%20in%20the%20liquor%20business%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20under%20the%20now-scrapped%20excise%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKavitha%20further%20told%20Sharath%20Chandra%20Reddy%20that%20the%20payments%20of%20upfront%20money%20of%20Rs%2025%20crore%20for%20wholesale%20business%20and%20Rs%205%20crore%20for%20each%20retail%20zone%20were%20to%20be%20made%20to%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20for%20getting%20liquor%20business%20and%20the%20same%20was%20to%20be%20paid%20to%20her%20associates%2C%20Arun%20R%20Pillai%20and%20Abhishek%20Boinpally%2C%20who%20would%20in%20turn%20coordinate%20with%20Vijay%20Nair%2C%20who%20was%20a%20representative%20of%20(Delhi%20Chief%20Minister)%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CBI%20told%20the%20court%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20sent%20Ms%20Kavitha%20to%20the%20CBI's%20custody%20till%20April%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20agency%2C%20in%20March%20and%20May%202021%2C%20when%20the%20excise%20policy%20was%20being%20formulated%2C%20Pillai%2C%20Boinpally%20and%20Butchibabu%20Gorantla%20stayed%20at%20the%20Hotel%20Oberoi%20in%20Delhi%20to%20swing%20the%20policy%20in%20their%20favour%20through%20Nair%20by%20inserting%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20receiving%20the%20assurance%20of%20support%20from%20Ms%20Kavitha%2C%20Aurobindo%20Reality%20and%20Infrastructure%20Private%20Limited%20paid%20Rs%2080%20lakh%20to%20her%20NGO%2C%20Telangana%20Jagruthi%2C%20under%20Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility%20(CSR)%20in%20March%202021%2C%20the%20CBI%20has%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20investigation%20has%20further%20revealed%20that%20in%20June-July%202021%2C%20K%20Kavitha%20had%20compelled%20Sharath%20Chandra%20Reddy%20to%20enter%20into%20a%20sale%20agreement%20with%20her%20for%20an%20agricultural%20land%20situated%20at%20Mahboob%20Nagar%2C%20Telangana%2C%20although%20he%20was%20not%20keen%20to%20purchase%20the%20said%20agricultural%20land%20and%20also%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20value%20of%20the%20said%20land%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Kavitha%20%26quot%3Binsisted%26quot%3B%20that%20Mr%20Reddy%20pay%20Rs%2014%20crore%20against%20the%20land%20and%20%26quot%3Bforced%26quot%3B%20him%20to%20enter%20into%20the%20sale%20agreement%20through%20Mahira%20Ventures%20Private%20Limited%2C%20one%20of%20the%20Aurobindo%20Group%20companies%2C%20in%20July%202021%2C%20the%20CBI%20has%20told%20the%20court%2C%20citing%20Mr%20Reddy's%20statement%20and%20its%20investigation%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20total%20payment%20of%20Rs%2014%20crore%20was%20made%20to%20Ms%20Kavitha%20through%20bank%20transactions%20--%20Rs%207%20crore%20in%20July%202021%20and%20another%20Rs%207%20crore%20in%20mid-November%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20has%20alleged%20that%20in%20November%20and%20December%20of%202021%2C%20Ms%20Kavitha%20asked%20Mr%20Reddy%20to%20pay%20Rs%2025%20crore%20(Rs%205%20crore%20per%20zone%20for%20the%20five%20retail%20zones%20allotted%20to%20him).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20leader%20had%20claimed%20that%20she%20herself%20had%20paid%20Rs%20100%20crore%20as%20upfront%20money%20on%20Mr%20Reddy's%20behalf%20to%20the%20AAP%20through%20Nair%20for%20getting%20favourable%20provisions%20in%20the%20excise%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20when%20Sarath%20Chandra%20Reddy%20showed%20his%20reluctance%20to%20pay%20the%20demanded%20money%2C%20K%20Kavitha%20threatened%20Sarath%20Chandra%20Reddy%20to%20harm%20his%20business%20in%20Telangana%20and%20Delhi%20under%20the%20excise%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20has%20alleged%2C%20citing%20Reddy's%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20alleged%20on%20March%2024%20that%20Mr%20Reddy's%20company%20had%20given%20Rs%2059.5%20crore%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20through%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20companies%20owned%20by%20Sarath%20Reddy%20bought%20electoral%20bonds%20and%20donated%20money%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Now%2C%20this%20money%20trail%20has%20been%20exposed%20in%20front%20of%20the%20country.%20Mr%20Reddy%20purchased%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%204.5%20crore%20while%20the%20excise%20policy%20was%20being%20formulated%20and%20after%20his%20arrest%2C%20he%20purchased%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%2055%20crore%20and%20the%20money%20went%20to%20the%20BJP.%20So%20the%20money%20trail%20that%20has%20been%20sought%20for%20the%20past%20two%20years%20is%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Delhi%20minister%20Atishi%20had%20alleged.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story