%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy-2-1711367448-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy-2-1711367448-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345727%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20influx%20of%20tourists%20in%20Ladakh%20generates%20a%20lot%20of%20thrash%20that%20the%20conversancy%20is%20trying%20to%20recycle%20and%20reduce%20through%20their%20efforts%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Namgail%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EExploring%20the%20majesty%20of%20the%20snow%20leopards%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20villagers%20who%20once%20moved%20around%20with%20fear%20in%20their%20eyes%20and%20a%20tremble%20in%20their%20steps%2C%20now%20have%20a%20newfound%20confidence.%20They%20no%20longer%20hate%20the%20feline.%20In%20fact%2C%20a%20major%20chunk%20of%20their%20incomes%20is%20generated%20by%20snow%20leopard-related%20tourism.%20To%20make%20up%20for%20the%20favour%2C%20the%20locals%20do%20not%20hunt%20the%20animals%20down%2C%20as%20they%20once%20did%2C%20thus%20allowing%20their%20population%20to%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20spearheading%20this%20harmony%20between%20beast%20and%20man%20has%20been%20the%20conservancy.%20But%20credit%20Namgail%20for%20leading%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335727%2Fintach-bengaluru-convenor-meera-iyer-restoring-forgotten-heritage-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20unique%20endeavour%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20this%2C%20and%20he%20says%20he%20owes%20his%20success%20to%20Wangchuk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20before%20I%20took%20over%20as%20director%20in%202013%2C%20I%20remember%20accompanying%20Mr%20Rinchen%20to%20the%20villages%20of%20Ladakh%20and%20speaking%20to%20the