0to%20protect%20their%20mountain%20environment.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20funds%20are%20created%20in%20a%20unique%20way%3A%2010%20percent%20of%20all%20homestays%E2%80%99%20income%20goes%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98village%20conservation%20fund%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20used%20by%20villagers%20for%20tree%20planting%2C%20garbage%20cleaning%2C%20and%20maintenance%20of%20their%20cultural%20heritage%2C%20such%20as%20mani%20walls%2C%20%3Cem%3Echortens%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20sacred%20juniper%20stands.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344962%2Fhow-to-start-a-homestay-in-india-rules-tips-from-owners-travel-business%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evillagers%20are%20encouraged%20to%20host%20guests%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20rotational%20basis.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20done%20so%20that%20no%20single%20family%20can%20monopolise%20the%20tourists.%20Because%20if%20that%20were%20to%20happen%2C%20it%20would%20create%20a%20disharmony%20in%20the%20village.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Namgail%20shares%2C%20the%20tourism%20model%20has%20been%20so%20successful%20that%20people%20across%20the%20Himalayas%20have%20taken%20inspiration%20from%20it%20and%20are%20replicating%20it.%20But%20regulation%20is%20important%2C%20he%20emphasises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20evening%20settles%20over%20Ladakh%2C%20the%20snow%20is%20tinged%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20blue%20and%20orange%2C%20a%20blend%20of%20the%20hues%20of%20the%20setting%20sun%20and%20dusk.%20As%20the%20locals%20go%20into%20their%20homes%2C%20bolt%20their%20doors%2C%20and%20warn%20the%20children%20to%20stay%20inside%2C%20the%20silent%20rustle%20of%20leaves%20goes%20unheard.%20So%20does%20the%20slither%20in%20the%20bushes%20and%20the%20shadow%20of%20a%20feline%20beginning%20its%20prowl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712827631000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy--1711367266.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345716%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Snow%20Leopard%20Conservancy%20India%20Trust%2C%20established%20by%20Rinchen%20Wangchuk%20and%20led%20by%20Dr%20Tsewang%20Namgail%2C%20champions%20the%20harmonious%20coexistence%20of%20villagers%20and%20snow%20leopards%20in%20Ladakh%20through%20its%20insurance%20schemes%20and%20sustainable%20tourism%20initiatives%2C%20fostering%20ecological%20balance%20in%20the%20region.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345716%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy-india-trust-tsewang-namgail-himalayan-homestays-ladakh%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Never%20Got%20to%20Read%E2%80%99%3A%2074-YO%20Grandmother%20Runs%20a%20Unique%20%E2%80%98Book%20Hotel%E2%80%99%20With%205000%20Books!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EClinking%20utensils%2C%20the%20gentle%20brewing%20of%20tea%2C%20and%20the%20lively%20chatter%20of%20people%20eagerly%20awaiting%20their%20food%20create%20a%20vibrant%20ambience%20within%20the%20eatery.%20Normally%2C%20the%20entire%20space%20is%20imbued%20with%20the%20tantalising%20aroma%20of%20delicious%20meals%20being%20prepared%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20However%2C%20this%20delightful%20scent%20often%20goes%20unnoticed%20by%20customers%20whose%20noses%20are%20typically%20buried%20in%20the%20books%20they%20are%20reading.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20most%20cheerful%20and%20wrinkly%20smile%2C%2074-year-old%20Bhimabai%20Jondhale%20observes%20the%20entire%20commotion.%20%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20a%20sense%20of%20pride%20when%20I%20watch%20all%20my%20customers%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332187%2Fbookclubs-in-indian-cities-like-kolkata-kochi-bengaluru-that-every-reader-should-join%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20reading%20keenly%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20almost%20forgetting%20what%20they%20were%20here%20for%20%E2%80%93%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFondly%20known%20as%20%3Cem%3EAaji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Bhimabai%20has%20been%20running%20her%20book%20restaurant%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EAjjichya%20Pustakancha%20Hotel%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20(Grandmother%E2%80%99s%20Hotel%20with%20Books)%2C%20since%202010%2C%20serving%20not%20only%20delicious%20meals%20but%20also%20offering%20free%20books%20to%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20place%20boasts%20a%20depository%20of%20over%205%2C000%20books%20in%20three%20different%20languages%20%E2%80%94%20Marathi%2C%20Hindi%2C%20and%20English.%20However%2C%20the%20origin%20story%20of%20this%20book%20hotel%20will%20surely%20melt%20your%20heart!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20undying%20love%20for%20reading%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20it%20is%20your%20birthday%20or%20anniversary%2C%20you%20are%20sure%20not%20to%20leave%20without%20a%20free%20book%20from%20Aaji%20Hotel.%20Located%20in%20Ozar%2C%20Nashik%20district%2C%20Bhimabai%E2%80%99s%20son%20helps%20her%20in%20the%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20hotel%20might%20be%20flourishing%20with%20colours%20and%20ample%20seating%20spaces%20today%2C%20it%20was%20only%20a%20makeshift%20spot%20for%20tea%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20only%20way%20for%20my%20mother%20to%20fill%20our%20stomachs.%20While%20she%20is%20a%20positive%20woman%20today%2C%20she%20has%20had%20her%20fair%20share%20of%20struggles%20back%20in%20the%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pravin%20Jondhale%2C%20Bhimabai%E2%80%99s%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20her%20early%20life%2C%20Bhimabai%20shares%20that%20she%20was%20merely%20in%20class%206%20when%20she%20was%20married%20off%20and%20sent%20to%20a%20small%20%3C