e%22%3A%22Why%20This%20Man%20is%20a%20Messiah%20for%20Hundreds%20of%20Tribals%20Dying%20Due%20to%20Incurable%20Silicosis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Mention%20of%20death.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20morning%2C%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Parvati%20Mardi%20would%20comb%20her%20hair%2C%20wear%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebindi%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20set%20out%20to%20work%20in%20a%20clean%20saree.%20But%20by%20the%20evening%2C%20she%20would%20be%20beyond%20recognisable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20worked%20in%20a%20ramming%20mass%20industry.%20As%20part%20of%20this%2C%20she%20would%20be%20exposed%20to%20silica%20dust%20all%20day.%20I%20remember%20that%20whenever%20she%20would%20come%20home%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20she%20would%20be%20completely%20covered%20in%20dust%20%E2%80%94%20her%20hair%2C%20clothes%2C%20all%20her%20body.%20It%20would%20get%20a%20little%20difficult%20for%20us%20to%20recognise%20her.%20The%20first%20thing%20ma%20would%20do%20was%20to%20take%20a%20bath%20before%20touching%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20her%20daughter%20Laxmi%20Mardi%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20tribal%20belts%20of%20Jharkhand%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20workers%20are%20forced%20to%20work%20in%20the%20ramming%20mass%20factories%20where%20quartzite%20stones%20are%20ground%20and%20powdered%20into%20dust%20and%20different-sized%20particles%20to%20prepare%20%E2%80%98ramming%20mass%E2%80%99.%20This%20is%20used%20to%20produce%20refractory%20items%20like%20fire%20bricks%20for%20steel%20industries%20and%20to%20manufacture%20insulators%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F191127%2Fdelhi-boy-innovation-recycling-glass-bottle-sand-construction-green-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esilica%20sand%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20huge%20quartzite%20stones%20are%20broken%20and%20milled%2C%20dust%20is%20released.%20This%20dust%20contains%20silicon%20dioxide%20which%20when%20inhaled%20over%20some%20time%20leads%20to%20silicosis%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20noticing%20that%20our%20mother%20would%20cough%20a%20lot%20and%20often%20complained%20about%20facing%20difficulty%20in%20breathing.%20Day%20by%20day%2C%20she%20also%20started%20losing%20weight%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20continued%20for%20four%20years%20until%20one%20day%20she%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20silicosis%20in%20April%202012.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20the%20first%20time%20we%20heard%20about%20the%20disease.%20We%20took%20her%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20but%20we%20were%20too%20young%20to%20understand%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20disease%20and%20how%20long%20she%20was%20going%20to%20stay%20with%20us.%20I%20was%2014%20years%20old%20then%2C%20and%20I%20was%20told%20that%20she%20would%20be%20home%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Parvati%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20silicosis%20in%202012.%20After%20a%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20she%20lost%20her%20succumbed%20to%20the%20disease.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345641%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EParvati%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20silicosis%20in%20April%202012.%20After%20a%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20she%20lost%20her%20succumbed%20to%20the%20disease.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20Laxmi%E2%80%99s%20mother%20could%20not%20be%20saved.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20was%20just%2033.%20All%20this%20pain%20was%20for%20Rs%2080-100%20wage%20per%20day.%20If%20I%20had%20known%20about%20the%20consequences%2C%20I%20would%20have%20never%20let%20my%20mother%20go%20to%20that%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20Laxmi%2C%20now%2028%2C%20says%20with%20a%20sigh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParvati%20was%20survived%20by%20her%20husband%2C%20her%20daughter%20Laxmi%2C%20and%20two%20younger%20sons.%20That%20day%2C%20Laxmi%20pledged%20to%20escape%20the%20life%20of%20drudgery%20%E2%80%94%20far%20from%20the%20ramming%20mass%20industry%20due%20to%20which%20at%20least%2010%2C000%20silicosis%20patients%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20past%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Laxmi%20works%20as%20a%20nursing%20officer%20and%20bears%20all%20the%20household%20responsibilities%20along%20with%20the%20college%20fees%20of%20her%20younger%20brothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20became%20possible%20with%20the%20support%20of%20Samit%20Carr%20sir.%20Firstly%2C%20his%20organisation%20bore%20our%20mother%E2%80%99s%20treatment%20cost%20of%20Rs%203.6%20lakh.%20Then%2C%20he%20encouraged%20me%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20nursing%20by%20getting%20a%20BSc%20degree.%20He%20also%20fought%20to%20get%20us%20a%20compensation%20amount%20of%20Rs%204%20lakh%20from%20the%20Government%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Laxmi%2C%20the%20Jharkhand-based%20non-profit%2C%20Occupational%20Safety%20And%20Health%20Association%20of%20Jharkhand%20(OSHAJ)%2C%20led%20by%20Samit%20Kumar%20Carr%2C%20has%20helped%20at%20least%2050%20kin%20of%20the%20workers%20who%20died%20of%20silicosis%20get%20compensation%20amount%20of%20Rs%204%20lakh%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20he%20has%20also%20helped%20the%20kin%20of%2022%20workers%20who%20died%20of%20silicosis%20in%20West%20Bengal%20get%20a%20compensation%20amount%20of%20Rs%204%20lakh%20each%2C%20and%2030%20silicosis-affected%20workers%20with%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20each.%20In%20addition%2C%20Rs%2010%20crore%20funds%20were%20sanctioned%20for%20pension%20and%20welfare%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20two%20decades%2C%20he%20has%20been%20actively%20fighting%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20silicosis%20patients%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20West%20Bengal.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20the%2068-year-old%20activist%20to%20learn%20how%20he%20is%20fighting%20authorities%20to%20help%20families%20cope%20with%20financial%20distress%20caused%20by%20the%20incurable%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1-1711118834.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samit%20Carr%20has%20helped%20at%20least%2050%20kin%20of%20the%20workers%20who%20died%20of%20silicosis%20get%20compensation%20amount%20of%20Rs%204%20lakh%20each.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1-1711118834.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1-1711118834-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1-1711118834-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1-1711118834-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1-1711118834-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345642%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESamit%20Carr%20has%20helped%20at%20least%2050%20kin%20of%20the%20workers%20who%20died%20of%20silicosis%20get%20compensation%20amount%20of%20Rs%204%20lakh%20each.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESilicosis%3A%20a%20silent%20killer%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20from%20Tripura%2C%20Samit%E2%80%99s%20family%20moved%20to%20Jamshedpur%20in%201955.%20While%20completing%20a%20draftsmanship%20course%20at%20Singhbhum%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20he%20remained%20unaware%20of%20the%20brutality%20experienced%20by%20workers%20exposed%20to%20silica%20dust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%202002%20that%20he%20first%20read%20about%20the%20rising%20deaths%20of%20silicosis%20patients%20in%20the%20East%20Singhbhum%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202003%2C%20I%20closely%20observed%20some%20silicosis%20patients.%20Most%20of%20them%20had%20difficulty%20in%20breathing%2C%20and%20could%20not%20sleep%20easily%20because%20of%20it.%20One%20of%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20daughters%20told%20us%20that%20she%20visited%20the%20site%20daily%20to%20give%20lunch%20to%20her%20father%2C%20but%20she%20always%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20recognise%20him%20as%20everyone%20would%20be%20covered%20in%20silica%20dust%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESilicosis%20is%20an%20incurable%20lung%20disease%20caused%20by%20the%20inhalation%20of%20dust%20containing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311633%2Fruhani-verma-built-indias-first-carbon-negative-recyclable-public-toilet-amritsar-airport%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esilica%20crystals%20%3C%2Fa%3Efound%20commonly%20in%20quartzite%2C%20granite%2C%20basalt%2C%20sandstone%2C%20agate%2C%20slate%20marble%2C%20and%20building%20materials%20like%20fire%20bricks%20and%20tiles.%20This%20exposes%20workers%20in%20dust-generating%20sites%20like%20factories%2C%20mining%20and%20construction%20sites%20to%20a%20high%20risk%20of%20contracting%20the%20disease%2C%20which%20leads%20to%20prolonged%20illness%20and%20painful%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-3-1711118905.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Silicosis%20is%20an%20incurable%20lung%20disease%20caused%20by%20the%20inhalation%20of%20dust%20containing%20silica%20crystals.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-3-1711118905.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-3-1711118905-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-3-1711118905-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-3-1711118905-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-3-1711118905-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345645%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESilicosis%20is%20an%20incurable%20lung%20disease%20caused%20by%20the%20inhalation%20of%20dust%20containing%20silica%20crystals.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20percentage%20of%20silicon%20dioxide%20in%20stones%2C%20the%20concentration%20of%20dust%20at%20the%20workplace%2C%20long%20working%20hours%2C%20dust%20exposed%20to%20them%20post%20duty%20hours%2C%20as%20well%20as%20poor%20immunity%20of%20workers%2C%20collectively%20makes%20them%20vulnerable%20to%20silicosis%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Samit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%20to%20closely%20watch%20the%20working%20conditions%20of%20these%20workers%20at%20the%20ramming%20mass%20industries.%20%E2%80%9CI%20went%20there%20to%20record%20a%20video%20of%20a%20woman%20worker%20who%20was%20covered%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310965%2Fautokast-ltd-kerala-government-turns-waste-sand-into-eco-friendly-silica-bricks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esilica%20dust%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20said%20that%20her%20husband%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20silicosis%20and%20the%20family%20exhausted%20all%20their%20money%20in%20treatment.%20But%2C%20he%20could%20not%20be%20saved%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20she%20refused%20to%20be%20recorded.%20She%20complained%20that%2C%20like%20me%2C%20many%20people%20visit%20them%2C%20click%20photos%2C%20and%20never%20come%20back.%20I%20was%20embarrassed.%20But%20that%20day%2C%20I%20promised%20myself%20that%20I%20would%20strive%20to%20get%20justice%20for%20these%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Samit%20has%20been%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20families%20of%20workers%20who%20died%20due%20to%20silicosis%20are%20compensated%20by%20the%20Government.%20In%202003%2C%20he%20established%20OSHAJ%20to%20advocate%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20such%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20even%20when%20I%20was%20accused%20of%20witchcraft%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20Samit%20travels%20from%20village%20to%20village%20in%20the%20tribal%20areas%20of%20Jharkhand%20and%20West%20Bengal%20to%20document%20the%20occupational%20and%20clinical%20histories%20of%20the%20workers%20and%20to%20collect%20chest%20X-ray%20plates%20from%20the%20workers%20for%20medical%20tests.%20After%20identifying%20patients%2C%20he%20encourages%20them%20to%20find%20alternate%20employment%20and%20helps%20their%20families%20get%20monetary%20compensation%20from%20the%20Government%20in%20case%20the%20patient%20is%20deceased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20process%20isn%E2%80%99t%20easy.%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20whenever%20I%20would%20voice%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20these%20workers%2C%20I%20would%20be%20thrown%20out%20of%20meetings.%20People%20started%20avoiding%20me%20and%20accusing%20me%20of%20practising%20witch-hunting.%20But%20eventually%2C%20they%20shared%20their%20documents%20with%20me%2C%20and%20I%20started%20fighting%20for%20the%20silicosis-affected%20community%20in%202006%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-2-1711118869.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samit%20has%20been%20on%20a%20mission%20advocate%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20tribal%20workers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-2-1711118869.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-2-1711118869-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-2-1711118869-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-2-1711118869-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-2-1711118869-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345643%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESamit%20has%20been%20on%20a%20mission%20advocate%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20tribal%20workers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20there%20has%20been%20immense%20politics%20right%20from%20the%20hospital%20level%20to%20the%20state%20officials.%20Many%20times%2C%20doctors%20also%20refuse%20to%20write%20correct%20reports%20because%20of%20pressure%20from%20higher%20authorities.%20We%20keep%20making%20rounds%20of%20the%20officials%20at%20the%20district%20levels%20to%20get%20these%20families%20their%20compensation%20rights%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20knocking%20on%20several%20official%20doors%2C%20Samit%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20(NHRC)%20and%20filed%20a%20petition%20on%208%20October%2C%202007%2C%20to%20seek%20their%20support%20for%20the%20relief%20of%20silicosis%20patients%20and%20their%20families.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20there%20is%20no%20formal%20amount%20of%20allocation%2C%20it%20directs%20the%20Government%20to%20provide%20Rs%204%20lakh%20compensation%20to%20the%20kin%20of%20dead%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2020%20years%2C%20Samit%20says%2C%20his%20organisation%20was%20able%20to%20source%20compensation%20amounts%20worth%20Rs%2013.52%20crore%20for%20workers%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20West%20Bengal.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20were%20able%20to%20raise%20Rs%2088%20lakh%20from%20donors%20in%2010%20years%20in%20both%20states%20for%20the%20treatment%20of%20silicosis%20patients%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamit%20says%20that%20the%20monetary%20support%20from%20the%20Government%20is%20extremely%20important%20for%20these%20families.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20breadwinners%20of%20the%20families%20die%2C%20young%20orphan%20children%20are%20forced%20to%20migrate%20for%20earning%20opportunities%20and%20lose%20their%20right%20to%20education.%20For%20them%2C%20the%20monetary%20compensation%20is%20a%20ray%20of%20hope%20for%20a%20better%20future.%20Many%20families%20have%20used%20these%20amounts%20to%20set%20up%20small%20businesses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20children%20but%20whenever%20I%20see%20young%20kids%20of%20dead%20workers%2C%20it%20aches%20my%20heart.%20Thankfully%2C%20with%20our%20small%20efforts%2C%20we%20can%20protect%20the%20future%20generations%20of%20some%20such%20workers.%20Now%20as%20I%20am%20getting%20old%2C%20I%20want%20to%20pass%20on%20my%20experience%20to%20dedicated%20people%20so%20that%20this%20work%20does%20not%20stop%20even%20after%20me.%20Otherwise%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20organisation%20by%202025.%20We%20also%20require%20decent%20funding%20support%20to%20continue%20this%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Samit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20support%20him%20in%20his%20mission%2C%20you%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20Samit%20Kumar%20Carr%20at%20roshniforlabour%40gmail.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fsociety%2Ftheres-a-scourge-of-silicosis-among-mine-and-factory-workers-in-jharkhand%2Farticle65092384.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBreathless%3A%20Silicosis%20is%20killing%20workers%20in%20Jharkhand%3A%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3EBy%20Vikram%20Raj%20for%20The%20Hindu%20published%20on%204%20March%202022.%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Samit%20Kumar%20Carr.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712749731000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345628%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20the%20past%2020%20years%2C%20Jharkhand's%20Samit%20Kumar%20Carr%20has%20helped%20families%20of%20workers%20who%20died%20due%20to%20incurable%20silicosis%20get%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%2013%20crores.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345628%2Fjharkhand-samit-kumar-carr-helps-silicosis-patients-get-monetary-compensation-from-government-nhrc%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karim%E2%80%99s%20to%20Peter%20Cat%3A%20The