20processes%20them%20and%20sends%20them%20to%20the%20hearing%20device%2C%20enabling%20the%20user%20to%20hear.%20The%20Bluetooth%20can%20also%20be%20connected%20to%20any%20other%20device%20like%20a%20mobile%20phone%2C%20TV%2C%20or%20laptop%2C%20helping%20children%20listen%20to%20classes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20solution%20for%20people%20with%20conductive%20hearing%20loss%20is%20usually%20a%20surgical%20implant%20called%20the%20BAHA%20implant%20(Bone-Anchored%20Hearing%20Aid)%2C%20which%20uses%20the%20same%20technology%20used%20in%20this%20hearing%20aid.%20The%20corresponding%20surgery%20generally%20costs%20Rs%208%20lakh%2C%20according%20to%20the%20founders%2C%20while%20this%20device%20costs%20Rs%2080%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20differentiator%20and%20patent%20is%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20use%20this%20technology%2C%20which%20is%20used%20in%20the%20surgery%20and%20military%20devices%2C%20for%20a%20non-surgical%20hearing%20aid%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20partnered%20with%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20Of%20Speech%20and%20Hearing%20in%20Mysuru%20for%20clinical%20trials%20and%20also%20received%20grants%20from%20the%20Union%20Government%20and%20State%20Government%20worth%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20to%20fund%20their%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20through%20this%20venture%2C%20the%20duo%20have%20provided%20the%20gift%20of%20hearing%20to%20over%2011%2C500%20children%20and%20adults%20across%20the%20country%20%E2%80%94%20the%20majority%20of%20which%20are%20through%20partnerships%20with%20corporations%20and%20CSR%20activities.%20They%20also%20partner%20with%20State%20Governments%20to%20distribute%20hearing%20aids%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Samagra%20Shiksha%20Abhiyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20HearNU%20is%20currently%20being%20exported%20to%20countries%20in%20Africa%2C%20with%20plans%20for%20global%20expansion%20supported%20by%20a%20granted%20