22_blank%5C%22%3EBengaluru%E2%80%99s%20lakes%3C%2Fa%3E%20hold%20sewage%2C%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20space%20for%20freshwater%20anymore.%20So%2C%20when%20rainfall%20happens%2C%20these%20lakes%20are%20filled%20with%20sewage%20to%20the%20brim%20and%20are%20not%20able%20to%20absorb%20that%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FBengaluru-Water-4-1712315003.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bengaluru's%20water%20scarcity%20is%20due%20to%20rampant%20urbanisation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FBengaluru-Water-4-1712315003.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FBengaluru-Water-4-1712315003-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FBengaluru-Water-4-1712315003-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FBengaluru-Water-4-1712315003-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FBengaluru-Water-4-1712315003-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346652%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERampant%20urbanisation%20has%20destroyed%20water%20bodies%20in%20the%20city%3A%20Photo%20of%20Bagmane%20Tech%20Park%20taken%20in%20April%202013%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20this%20impacts%20the%20lake%20system%2C%20and%20thereby%20the%20groundwater.%20We%20are%20one%20of%20the%20most%20intense%20borewelling%20communities%20in%20the%20world.%20Nowhere%20else%20will%20you%20see%20so%20many%20borewells%20being%20dug%20everywhere%2C%20which%20technically%20depletes%20all%20the%20groundwater%20reserves%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arun%20Krishnamurthy%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F104777%2Ftamil-nadu-drought-nagapattinam%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEnvironmentalist%20Foundation%20of%20India%20(EFI)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20revives%20water%20bodies.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20groundwater%20reserves%20depleted%20and%20lakes%20holding%20sewage%2C%20which%20also%20means%20there%20is%20no%20space%20for%20freshwater%20from%20the%20monsoon%20rains%20to%20flow%20into%20%E2%80%94%20all%20these%20factors%20put%20together%20are%20causing%20this%20kind%20of%20drought.%20Bengaluru%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20first%20though%20given%20that%20Chennai%20went%20through%20something%20similar%20in%202018-19.%20Any%20urban%20pocket%20in%20India%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20affected%20by%20such%20a%20scenario%20given%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20clear%20understanding%20of%20surface%20water%20bodies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20do%20you%20go%20about%20revving%20these%20water%20bodies%20and%20improving%20the%20groundwater%20level%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArun%20speaks%20of%20Devanahalli%20Kere%2C%20the%20first%20lake%20EFI%20took%20up%20in%20Bengaluru%20for%20revival%20in%202022.%20As%20an%20organisation%2C%20they%20have%20largely%20focussed%20on%20suburban%20Bengaluru%20rather%20than%20the%20main%20city%20area.%20This%20is%20because%20the%20suburban%20lakes%20were%20heading%20on%20the%20current%20path%20of%20the%20city%20lakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fr4iFfE90g_o%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fr4iFfE90g_o%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20prevent%20any%20kind%20of%20contamination%20or%20encroachment%2C%20we%20have%20taken%20up%20water%20bodies%20in%20Ramanagara%2C%20Tumkur%2C%20and%20Bengaluru%20(Rural)%20districts%2C%20and%20the%20closest%20such%20lake%20to%20the%20main%20city%20is%20the%20Devanahalli%20Lake.%20Within%20Karahalli%2C%20which%20is%20next%20to%20Devanahalli%2C%20we%20have%20revived%20at%20least%20five%20water%20bodies.%20What%20we%20have%20achieved%20is%20deepening%20these%20water%20bodies%20to%20increase%20storage%20capacity%2C%20regulating%20their%20inlet%20and%20outlet%20channels%20so%20that%20there%20is%20a%20free%20flow%20of%20water%2C%20and%20we%20have%20also%20ensured%20recharge%20wells%20have%20been%20created%20in%20all%20these%20systems%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Arun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBuilding%20these%20recharge%20wells%20is%20all%20about%20ensuring%20there%20is%20enough%20groundwater%20percolation.%20Creating%20a%20water%20holding%20structure%20based%20on%20the%20soil%20structure%2C%20understanding%20its%20utilisation%20value%20to%20the%20region%2C%20and%20creating%20percolation%20trenches%20and%20recharge%20wells%20have%20all%20been%20our%20key%20focus%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20Devanahalli%2C%20Karahalli%2C%20the%20Baddihalli%20Lake%20in%20Tumkur%20city%2C%20or%20the%20Hulikunte%20lake.%20EFI%20has%20restored%20all%20these%20water%20bodies%20with%20this%20larger%20point%20in%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20impact%20of%20all%20these%20initiatives%20on%20the%20communities%20who%20live%20near%20these%20lakes%20has%20been%20visible.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20borewells%20are%20not%20as%20dry%20as%20what%20we%20hear%20from%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20city.%20These%20lakes%2C%20which%20were%20often%20used%20as%20dumping%20sites%2C%20are%20now%20no%20longer%20perceived%20as%20such.%20People%20want%20to%20protect%20them.%20When%20droughts%20occur%2C%20people%20realise%20and%20understand%20the%20significance%20of%20these%20lakes%20better%20and%20they%20volunteer%20with%20us%20to%20maintain%20and%20upkeep%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20goes%20into%20the%20maintenance%20and%20upkeep%20of%20these%20water%20bodies%20includes%20the%20prevention%20of%20encroachment%2C%20dumping%20of%20garbage%2C%20and%20sewage%20entering%20that%20lake%2C%20and%20keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20water%20body%20in%20general%20to%20maintain%20its%20quality%20and%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20important%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20canals%20interlinking%20these%20lakes%20are%20well%20maintained.%20As%20Arun%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CInterlinking%20of%20water%20bodies%20at%20an%20NGO%20level%20is%20impossible%20simply%20because%20between%20two%20lakes%2C%20the%20canal%20system%20that%20exists%20will%20largely%20fall%20under%20Government%20land%20or%20private%20land.%20We%20can%20recommend%20Government%20agencies%20to%20update%20these%20canal%20systems.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20recommendations%20to%20the%20Government%20will%20also%20include%20properly%20mapping%20these%20water%20bodies%2C%20watershed%20wetlands%2C%20and%20preventing%20encroachment%20where%20necessary%20and%20focusing%20on%20the%20structural%20integrity%20of%20freshwater%20systems.%20We%20desperately%20need%20the%20latter%20today.%20But%20we%20will%20not%20be%20in%20a%20position%20to%20revive%20these%20interlinking%20areas%20completely%20simply%20because%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20bandwidth%20to%20talk%20to%20all%20the%20landowners%20and%20remove%20encroachment%20or%20more.%20What%20is%20possible%20on%20our%20level%2C%20however%2C%20is%20inlet-outlet%20regulation%20within%20the%20lake%E2%80%99s%20periphery%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20lakes%20in%20the%20main%20city%20beyond%20redemption%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20not%20beyond%20redemption%20if%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20political%20will%2C%20heavy%20scientific%20backing%2C%20and%20complete%20community%20understanding%20of%20the%20problem.%20Even%20if%20one%20of%20these%20elements%20is%20missing%2C%20these%20lakes%20cannot%20be%20saved%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FwEV7pANn0gw%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FwEV7pANn0gw%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERecharge%20wells%20over%20borewells%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20lakes%2C%20another%20key%20element%20in%20raising%20the%20groundwater%20level%20and%20establishing%20a%20surplus%20water%20supply%20is%20open%20recharge%20wells.%20An%20open%20%5Brecharge%5D%20well%20is%20simply%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20ground%20that%20allows%20access%20to%20water%20underground.%20These%20wells%20are%20used%20to%20extract%20water%20from%20the%20shallowest%20level%20%E2%80%94%20typically%20found%20in%20unconfined%20shallow%20aquifers%20where%20water%20is%20held%20without%20any%20pressure.%20These%20aquifers%20receive%20water%20when%20rain%20or%20other%20surface%20water%20percolates%20down%20into%20it%20%E2%80%94%20a%20process%20known%20as%20recharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC5Q44fJSnPZ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC5Q44fJSnPZ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC5Q44fJSnPZ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20zenrainman%20(%40zenrainman)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Vishwanath%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20we%20speak%2C%20well%20diggers%20working%20with%20BBMP%20(Bruhat%20Bengaluru%20Mahanagara%20Palike)%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20shallow%20aquifer%20management%20project%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20recently%20cleaned%20up%20a%20well%20in%20a%20particular%20locality%20very%20close%20to%20my%20house%20called%20Nandini%20Layout.%20That%20%5Bopen%20recharge%5D%20well%20today%20gives%20one%20lakh%20litres%20of%20water%20%5Ba%20day%5D%20and%20supports%20500-700%20resident%20families%20for%20non-potable%20use.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20north%20of%20the%20city%2C%20we%20at%20Biome%20Environmental%20Trust%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20CSR%20initiative%2C%20cleaned%20up%20six%20wells%2C%20and%20in%20two%20of%20them%2C%20the%20women%20in%20the%20area%20told%20us%20not%20to%20install%20a%20motor.%20They%20wanted%20to%20draw%20the%20water%20manually.%20Today%2050%20to%2070%20families%20in%20the%20area%20can%20draw%20water%20from%20the%20well.%20In%20two%20other%20wells%2C%20the%20town%20municipal%20council%20have%20installed%20pumps%2C%20and%20so%20far%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20got%2070%20million%20litres%20of%20water%20for%20their%20town%20municipal%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishwanath%20goes%20on%20to%20elaborate%20on%20other%20such%20projects%20his%20trust%20has%20embarked%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20claims%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20Devanahalli%20township%2C%20where%20the%20international%20airport%20is%20located%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20able%20to%20work%20with%20several%20NGOs%20and%20partners%20who%20cleaned%20up%20a%20lake%2C%20which%20is%20now%20filled%20with%20rainwater%20and%20well-treated%20wastewater%20from%20Bengaluru.%20This%20water%20filters%20into%20the%20earth%20and%20there%20is%20an%20old%20open%20well%20we%20have%20revived.%20That%20well%20gives%202.5%20lakh%20litres%20of%20water%20a%20day%20to%20which%20we%20have%20attached%20a%20water%20treatment%20plant%20and%20are%20supplying%20that%20water%20to%20the%20town%20of%20Devanahalli.%20We%20have%20also%20constructed%20filter%20borewells%2C%20which%20are%20shallow%20borewells%20which%20go%2080%20to%20100%20feet%20deep%2C%20and%20they%20have%20a%20porous%20casing%20and%20function%20like%20open%20recharge%20wells.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWherever%20we%20do%20good%20%5Bopen%5D%20recharge%20%5Bwells%5D%20and%20lakes%20are%20revived%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20shallow%20aquifer%20which%20comes%20back%20to%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FeXn1Lx725Js%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FeXn1Lx725Js%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishwanath%20believes%20that%20every%20building%20in%20Bengaluru%20can%20be%20part%20of%20the%20solution.%20%E2%80%9CTake%20all%20the%20rainwater%20you%20can%2C%20store%20it%20in%20a%20sump%20tank%20and%20reuse%20it.%20If%20you%20have%20excess%20rainwater%2C%20please%20make%20sure%20that%20this%20goes%20into%20recharge%20wells%20so%20that%20the%20shallow%20aquifer%20is%20full%20and%20then%20you%20dip%20into%20it%20in%20times%20of%20need.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20overall%20goal%20of%20our%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F173853%2Fbengaluru-ground-water-crisis-well-digging-day-zero-zenrainman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOne%20Million%20Wells%20for%20Bengaluru%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20initiative.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%2C%20why%20weren%E2%80%99t%20these%20solutions%20put%20in%20place%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20city%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20piped%20connections%20and%20are%20today%20struggling%20for%20water%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20because%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20groundwater%20management%20plan.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20groundwater%20authority%20which%20integrates%20groundwater%20into%20our%20drinking%20water%20needs.%20We%20just%20have%20someone%20who%20permits%20us%20to%20drill%20borewells.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20much%20groundwater%20exists%20below%20our%20feet%2C%20where%20are%20the%20recharge%20zones%2C%20where%20we%20retain%20them%2C%20how%20much%20water%20are%20we%20drawing%20from%20each%20sub-aquifer%2C%20and%20how%20we%20draw%20a%20balance%20between%20demand%20and%20supply.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20groundwater%20cell%20in%20the%20BWSSB%20or%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20groundwater%20plan%20or%20an%20aquifer%20management%20plan%2C%20what%20happens%20is%20everyone%20is%20tapping%20into%20the%20aquifer%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Vishwanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20are%20seeing%20today%20in%20Bengaluru%20is%20competitive%20drilling.%20In%20parts%20of%20the%20city%2C%20people%20have%20dug%20borewells%20as%20deep%20as%201%2C800%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CEverybody%20is%20taking%20water%20out.%20Nobody%20is%20putting%20water%20back%20in.%20Unless%20we%20create%20the%20right%20type%20of%20institution%2C%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20groundwater%20and%20manages%20it%20as%20a%20common%20pool%20resource%20for%20all%20citizens%2C%20this%20is%20what%20will%20happen%20and%20is%20happening.%20The%20problem%20is%20institutional%20and%20lies%20in%20governance%20or%20lack%20thereof%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Vishwanath.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20959px)%20100vw%2C%20959px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FS-Vishwanath-Lake-Water-1-1712316034.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22959%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Can%20we%20solve%20Bengaluru's%20Water%20scarcity%20problem%3F%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FS-Vishwanath-Lake-Water-1-1712316034.jpg%20959w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FS-Vishwanath-Lake-Water-1-1712316034-300x198.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FS-Vishwanath-Lake-Water-1-1712316034-500x330.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FS-Vishwanath-Lake-Water-1-1712316034-768x507.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FS-Vishwanath-Lake-Water-1-1712316034-150x99.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346663%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22633%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESolution%20to%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20Water%20Scarcity%20Problem%3A%20A%20well%20fed%20by%20a%20shallow%20aquifer%20revived%20through%20rainwater%20harvesting%20and%20recharge.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20groundwater%20levels%20are%20the%20problem%20in%20the%20periphery%20of%20the%20main%20city%2C%20Vishwanath%20advocates%20the%20need%20to%20move%20from%20competitive%20drilling%20to%20cooperative%20filling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20it%E2%80%99s%20cooperative%20filling%2C%20we%20need%20to%20fill%20the%20lakes%20and%20make%20recharge%20wells%20so%20that%20when%20the%20rains%20come%2C%20the%20water%20flows%20into%20the%20aquifer.%20That%20is%20the%20solution.%20Currently%2C%20we%20have%20excellent%20tertiary%20treated%20water%20in%20some%20of%20our%20wastewater%20treatment%20plants%20like%20in%20Jakkur%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F91618%2Fshakespeare-cubbon-park-bardolators-bangalore%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECubbon%20Park%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20etc%20where%20you%20can%20drink%20the%20water%20from%20the%20sewage%20treatment%20plants%20(STPs)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20take%20this%20water%20and%20fill%20our%20lakes%20quickly%2C%20which%20are%20now%20dry%2C%20so%20that%20the%20aquifer%20gets%20recharged.%20We%20should%20start%20preparing%20to%20clean%20up%20our%20rainwater%20harvesting%20systems%20and%20make%20sure%20new%20recharge%20wells%20are%20dug%20so%20that%20when%20the%20summer%20rains%20come%2C%20those%20drops%20of%20water%20are%20pushed%20into%20the%20aquifer.%20If%20this%20is%20done%2C%20we%20can%20overcome%20the%20problem%20in%20the%20short%20run%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FLn5ZwJofmNE%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FLn5ZwJofmNE%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHarvesting%20rainwater%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98One%20Million%20Wells%20for%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99%20initiative%20was%20conceived%20and%20facilitated%20by%20Biome%20Environmental%20Trust%20to%20solve%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20water%20crisis%20sometime%20in%202005.%20The%20movement%E2%80%99s%20main%20objective%20has%20been%20to%20enable%20households%20across%20the%20city%20to%20conform%20to%20the%20law%20mandating%20rainwater%20harvesting.%20And%20this%20also%20includes%20%E2%80%9Ca%20recharge%20well%E2%80%9D%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20various%20projects%20like%20%E2%80%98One%20Million%20Wells%20for%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99%20and%20other%20rainwater%20harvesting%20initiatives%2C%20we%20asked%20Vishwanath%20to%20explain%20their%20impact%20on%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20the%20Rail%20Wheel%20Factory%20in%20Yelahanka%2C%20where%20they%20have%20done%20good%20rainwater%20harvesting%2C%20their%20open%20recharge%20wells%20are%20giving%20them%20two%20lakh%20litres%20of%20water%20a%20day.%20At%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F267840%2Fiim-cat-tips-tricks-hacks-things-to-know-work-experience-selection-process-quora%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIIM%20Bangalore%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20rainwater%20harvesting%20has%20been%20done%2C%20their%20borewells%20are%20giving%20them%20water%20at%20300%20to%20400%20feet%2C%20and%20they%E2%80%99re%20getting%20enough%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Vishwanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWherever%20rainwater%20harvesting%20is%20done%20well%20and%20in%20concentrated%20amounts%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20problem.%20Their%20aquifers%20are%20full%20and%20have%20water%20despite%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20drought.%20Even%20in%20Cubbon%20Park%2C%20where%20people%20and%20organisations%20have%20done%20rainwater%20harvesting%20like%20Friends%20of%20Lakes%2C%20there%20is%20water%20in%20open%20recharge%20wells.%20Rainwater%20harvesting%20can%20send%20in%20X%20amount%20of%20water%20but%20your%20withdrawal%20should%20be%20less%20than%20X.%20If%20your%20draw%20is%202X%2C%20then%20even%20this%20won%E2%80%99t%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20that%2C%20there%20are%20more%20concerns%20about%20the%20rainwater%20harvesting%20(RWH)%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20city.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20BWSSB%20Amendment%20Act%2C%202011%2C%20made%20RWH%20mandatory%20for%20all%20properties%20on%20plots%20measuring%2060%C3%9740%20sq%20ft%20and%20above%2C%20and%20new%20properties%20coming%20up%20on%2030%C3%9740%20sq%20ft%20sites.%20In%202015%2C%20penalties%20were%20introduced%20for%20properties%20that%20didn%E2%80%99t%20comply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%207%20December%202023%20report%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcitizenmatters.in%2Fbengaluru-rainwater-harvesting-bwssb-kscst-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECitizen%20Matters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20media%20publication%2C%20reporter%20Navya%20PK%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6the%20city%20currently%20has%2010.8%20lakh%20properties%20with%20water%20connections%2C%20but%20only%201.9%20lakh%20(nearly%2018%25)%20of%20them%20have%20implemented%20RWH.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnother%2039%2C703%20properties%20have%20been%20identified%20for%20non-implementation%20and%20are%20paying%20penalties%20every%20month.%20These%20properties%20include%20individual%20homes%2C%20apartments%20(each%20apartment%20is%20counted%20as%20a%20single%20connection)%2C%20and%20commercial%20properties%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20compliance%20is%20a%20serious%20issue%20even%20though%20installing%20a%20RWH%20system%20is%20neither%20very%20complicated%20nor%20cost-intensive.%20Vishwanath%20notes%20that%20residents%20should%20build%20robust%20RWH%20systems%20so%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20face%20quality-related%20concerns%20down%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20believes%20that%20there%20are%20enough%20quality%20materials%20and%20competent%20plumbers%20present%20in%20the%20market.%20An%20individual%20home%20can%20install%20a%20RWH%20system%20for%20as%20little%20as%20Rs%205%2C000.%20Even%20if%20you%20insist%20on%20using%20a%20high-quality%20filter%2C%20it%20can%20be%20done%20within%20Rs%2015%2C000%2C%20provided%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20build%20a%20new%20sump%2C%20he%20argues.%20And%20the%20benefits%20of%20this%20system%20are%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20home%2C%20we%20have%20rainwater%20harvesting%20systems%20that%20are%20operating%20optimally.%20Even%20though%20the%20last%20rains%20in%20the%20city%20were%20in%20November%2C%20our%201%2C000-litre%20rain%20barrel%20still%20has%20enough%20water%20for%20our%20drinking%20and%20cooking%20needs%20till%20June%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Vishwanath.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20question%20of%20compliance%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbangaloremirror.indiatimes.com%2Fbangalore%2Fothers%2Fare-you-harvesting-rainwater%2Farticleshow%2F106646319.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBangalore%20Mirror%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%20by%20Sridhar%20Vivan%20on%209%20January%202024%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20staggering%20Rs%2021.24%20crore%20was%20collected%20as%20penalties%20for%20non-compliance%20with%20rainwater%20harvesting%20regulations%20until%20November-end%20last%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20non-implementation%20of%20RWH%20in%20residential%20properties%2C%20fines%20start%20from%2025%25%20of%20their%20water%20bill%20for%20the%20first%20three%20months%2C%20and%2050%25%20afterwards.%20For%20non-residential%20properties%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%2050%25%20and%20100%25%20of%20the%20water%20bill%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishwanath%20argues%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20tough%20to%20expect%20100%25%20compliance%20and%20argues%20that%20penalising%20residents%20may%20not%20be%20the%20way%20forward.%20Instead%2C%20he%20recommends%20that%20people%20should%20want%20to%20set%20up%20a%20RWH%20system%20in%20their%20homes%20after%20a%20process%20of%20education%20and%20communication.%20And%20the%20benefits%20of%20installing%20such%20a%20system%20in%20each%20Bengaluru%20home%20would%20be%20immense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Bengaluru%20Water%20Datajam%20organised%20last%20month%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopencity.in%2Fbengaluru-water-datajam-march-2024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpen%20City%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20civic%20tech%20project%2C%20found%20that%20based%20on%20rainfall%20data%20from%202022%2C%20%E2%80%9C456%20Million%20Litres%20per%20Day(MLD)%20could%20have%20been%20harvested%20in%20Bengaluru%20from%20the%20rooftops%2C%20which%20is%2025%25%20of%20the%20water%20demand%20of%20the%20city%20%E2%80%93%201890%20MLD.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC347a5myHh8%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC347a5myHh8%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%2